sherpa-onnx
===========

Project: sherpa-onnx
Upstream: https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx
Version used by LanXin Android: 1.13.4
Packaging: official Android AAR
  - sherpa-onnx-static-link-onnxruntime-1.13.4.aar
  - (alternative) sherpa-onnx-1.13.4.aar

License: Apache License 2.0
Full text: https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx/blob/master/LICENSE

Copyright: sherpa-onnx authors and contributors (k2-fsa / Xiaomi and others).

Notes for LanXin:
- Runtime native libraries are packaged into the APK via the AAR (Gradle download at build time).
- ASR model weights (ONNX / tokens) are NOT redistributed in this repository; users download
  them separately into LanXin/asr/ (see docs/voice-asr.md and docs/debug-assets.md).
- Bundled ONNX Runtime inside the static-link AAR is used by sherpa-onnx ASR.
  The app may also depend on Microsoft onnxruntime-android for embeddings; packaging
  pickFirsts handle duplicate libonnxruntime.so when both are present.
